N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 68.7 - Identification requirements

State Regulations

Each SMV emblem shall contain on the front or back the
manufacturer's name or trade-name which shall be the same name under which the
emblem has been certified. In lieu of marking or labeling the emblem, this same
information must appear on the package in which it is first sold to a purchaser
or user in this State. Notes
